    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2012-05-09</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2012-06-09T14:36:46Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Municipal Bond Market Support Act of 2012 - Amends Internal Revenue Code provisions relating to the small issuer exemption from interest expense allocation rules for financial institutions to: (1) permanently increase from $10 million to $30 million the annual limit on the amount of tax-exempt obligations that a small issuer may issue, and (2) allow an inflation adjustment to such increased limit amount after 2012.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
